{"search_data": "AssamAssam Gyan Deepika Scheme \u2013 E-Bikes / Free Admission / Free Uniforms / Subsidy on Education LoansAssam Gyan Deepika Scheme announced in budget 2019-2020, students to get admission fee waiver upto degree level, free uniforms to class 9th & 10th students, E-Bikes to girls & Rs. 50,000 subsidy on education loansAssam Gyan Deepika Yojana 2019The important features and highlights of Gyan Deepika Scheme are as follows:-The state govt. will provide admission fee waiver upto Degree Level whose parental annual income is less than Rs. 1 lakh.Free uniforms would be given to all the Class IX (9th) and X (10th) class students.Free Textbooks would be given to all the students till class XII.E-Bike would be distributed to girls who secure first division in higher secondary examination. These battery operated e-bikes would help girls in commuting to their places of higher studies.Assam govt. will also provide Rs. 50,000 subsidy on all education loans.To provide free admission, the state govt. will enhance parental income level of Rs. 1 lakh to Rs. 2 lakh in the upcoming months. Assam govt. will also provide free textbooks to students upto degree level (Arts, Science, Commerce) from present level of class XII in the upcoming months.The official tweets at the Himanta Biswa Sharma twitter handler are shown below:-#AssamBudget2019\u099c\u09cd\u099e\u09be\u09a8 \u09a6\u09c0\u09aa\u09bf\u0995\u09be\u2022\u09a8\u09ac\u09ae \u0986\u09f0\u09c1 \u09a6\u09b6\u09ae\u09ae\u09be\u09a8\u09f0 \u099b\u09be\u09a4\u09cd\u09f0-\u099b\u09be\u09a4\u09cd\u09f0\u09c0\u09f0 \u09ac\u09be\u09ac\u09c7 \u09ac\u09bf\u09a8\u09be\u09ae\u09c2\u09b2\u09c0\u09af\u09bc\u09be \u09b8\u09ae\u09ac\u09c7\u09b6 (Uniform)\u2022\u09ac\u09be\u09f0\u09cd\u09b7\u09bf\u0995 \u09e8 \u09b2\u09be\u0996 \u099f\u0995\u09be\u09a4\u0995\u09c8 \u0995\u09ae \u0986\u09af\u09bc\u09f0 \u09aa\u09f0\u09bf\u09af\u09bc\u09be\u09b2\u09f0 \u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09c7\u09a4\u09cd\u09f0\u09a4 \u09aa\u09cd\u09f0\u09af\u09cb\u0