aries have been paid stipend under Deen Dayal Divyangyan Sahayjya Asoni Yojana amounting to Rs. 138 crore. An outlay of Rs. 200 crore for these initiatives in Assam Budget 2019 has been allocated.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}